seng202.team1

Class UserAccountModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • seng202.team1.UserAccountModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class UserAccountModel
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Model class of a user. Has 4 constructors for various options, including account type specification and optional gender. Flags any user who is under 13 (for data usage laws). Implements Serializable to allow Users to be persistently saved.
